* Elisedd Welsh
* Eliya (එලියා) Sinhala
* Eliyas (Ілияс) Kazakh
* Eliyahu, Eliya (אֵלִיָּהוּ, אליה) Biblical Hebrew, Hebrew
* Elyās, Ilyās, Eliya (, ) Arabic
* Elliot, Elliott English
* Ellis English, Welsh (anglicised)
* Helias Ecclesiastical Latin
